title: Juniors Café
overview: When the affluent Hayes family moves to Attaway to take over the beloved Junior's Cafe, they're determined to turn it into the flagship of their new coffee empire. Siblings Jackson and Mallory will navigate the ups and downs of running a coffee shop alongside siblings Felix and Tara, testing their relationships—both familial and professional. Can they blend their ambitions with the realities of their new small-town life without spilling the beans?
